Well, with my 1-Handed weapon, my DPS drops from 34-40 to 15-25.  Adding in crappy 95+ damage bashes doesn't compensate for that.<br>
<br>
In order to bash with a 2-handed weapon, I have to have my epic (the real one, not the ND that I use), or I have to be level 59 and spend a bunch of AA points.  Guess what?  Bash damage from our epic and from people using the AA ability didn't get upgraded with the patch. <p><center>
