    I do know that she was stealing aggro often with the processes.  The process message popped often, sometimes several times in a row.  I think she had fun getting to melee some as most of the times she has grouped with me, she has had to spend it rezzing my dumb ass or CHing me on one of my busted pulls.<br>
   Worse thing for me during the fights was worrying about whether anyone was paying attention to my hitpoint bar as it began dipping lower (druids were debating whether the snare on their epics was really gone or not and what dots to stack).  I believe this will be a situational thing that will either pass or get nerfed.  But only my opinion. <p>Tiket Kouryuu
